snippet.title: KUBO 3 (NES homebrew)
snippet.description:
Vidéo de KUBO 3, mon nouveau jeu NES.
Disponible ici: https://dale-coop.itch.io/kubo-3-nes-game-by-sj-games
Interview pour la TV lors de la sortie de l'édition physique : https://youtu.be/q6SKDqmlbWA

Video of KUBO 3, my new NES game.
Download the ROM here: https://dale-coop.itch.io/kubo-3-nes-game-by-sj-games
Interview for French TV: https://youtu.be/q6SKDqmlbWA

-----------------
Current version KUBO 3 (rev C)
Made by Seiji Games
with NESmaker The New 8bit Heroes
Code: dale_coop
Soundtrack: Raftronaut
